org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.nodesource.policy

Class TimeSlotPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.nodesource.policy.NodeSourcePolicy
      • org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.nodesource.policy.TimeSlotPolicy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.objectweb.proactive.Active, org.objectweb.proactive.InitActive, NodeSourcePlugin

    public class TimeSlotPolicy
extends NodeSourcePolicy
implements org.objectweb.proactive.InitActive
    Allocated nodes for specified time slot: from "acquire time" to "release time" with specified period. Remove nodes preemptively if "preemptive" parameter is set to true.
    If period is zero then acquisition will be performed once.
    NOTE: difference between acquire and release time have to be bigger than time required to nodes all acquisition. Period have to be enough to release all nodes.
